<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="7Jun1928"><font color="red">7 June 1928</font> <i>James Joyce Archive</i> (Sylvia Beach to Crosby Gaige): Mr Joyce asked me to send you the following additional corrections in &ldquo;Anna Livia Plurabelle&rdquo;: page 1 line 27 for &ldquo;lough&rdquo; read &ldquo;Loch&rdquo; / page 5 line 13 for &ldquo;alas alacs&rdquo; read &ldquo;aleffe, the leaks&rdquo; </div>
